        "Fact:- The humidity levels are often higher at dawn, making the air feel softer on your skin. This extra moisture can be soothing for your respiratory system and your external senses.",
        "Fact:- A morning routine creates a predictable structure that reduces decision fatigue for your brain. Knowing your first few steps allows your mind to stay in a state of ease.",
