        "Fact:- Honey never spoils and archeologists have found edible honey in ancient Egyptian tombs that are thousands of years old. It is one of the few foods that lasts forever naturally.",
        "Fact:- Crows are known to remember human faces and can hold grudges against people who have treated them poorly. Conversely, they will also bring gifts to humans who are kind to them.",
        "Fact:- A blue whale’s heart is the size of a bumper car and is large enough for a human to swim through its arteries. It is the largest animal to ever live on Earth.",
