        "Fact:- A group of badgers is called a cete. Badgers are powerful diggers that live in complex underground burrow systems called setts.",
        "Fact:- Dolphins have been known to rescue humans and other animals from shark attacks. They are altruistic creatures that show a high level of empathy and cooperation.",
