        "Fact:- Dogs have a sense of time and can predict when their owners are coming home based on their daily routine. They are very sensitive to the patterns of their environment.",
        "Fact:- A group of emus is called a mob. Emus are large, flightless birds from Australia that can run at speeds of up to thirty miles per hour.",
