        "Fact:- Magnesium is a mineral that helps muscles relax and supports the nervous system. Eating foods high in magnesium can help reduce physical tension.",
        "Fact:- Focusing on five things you can see is a technique used to stop overthinking. It pulls your attention away from internal fears and back to the world.",
        "Fact:- Lavender oil has been scientifically shown to have a calming effect on the brain. Smelling it can help reduce the physical symptoms of nervousness.",
        "Fact:- Lack of sleep can significantly increase the levels of anxiety you feel the next day. Rest is a vital tool for emotional and mental regulation.",
