        "Motivation:- Do not give anyone the satisfaction of seeing you lose your composure. Staying cool is the ultimate victory over those who try to upset you.",
        "Motivation:- Every minute you spend being angry is sixty seconds of happiness you can never get back. Value your time enough to walk away from negativity.",
