        "Motivation:- Do not allow a bad moment to turn into a bad day or a bad week. Reset your mind right now and choose to focus on something positive.",
        "Motivation:- The person who can stay calm under pressure is the one who will lead others. Lead yourself toward peace and others will follow your example.",
        "Motivation:- You are worth more than the frustration you are feeling in this exact moment. Remind yourself of your value and let the irritation melt away.",
        "Motivation:- Peace is a conscious choice that you must make every single morning and evening. Choose it now and feel the tension leave your shoulders.",
        "Motivation:- Rage is a heavy coat that makes it very difficult to walk toward your destiny. Take it off and travel light with a heart full of hope.",
        "Motivation:- Focus on the solution instead of dwelling on the problem that made you upset. Action is the best remedy for a mind clouded by anger.",
