        "Motivation:- Rest is not a sign of weakness but a necessary step for your recovery. Your tired mind deserves the same kindness you give to everyone else.",
        "Motivation:- You have pushed through so much today and it is okay to stop now. Tomorrow will be a new chance to shine with fresh energy.",
        "Motivation:- Taking a break does not mean you are quitting your long journey. It means you are being smart enough to recharge your beautiful spirit.",
        "Motivation:- Your worth is not defined by how much you can do when you are exhausted. You are a human being who deserves peace and quiet moments.",
        "Motivation:- Allow your heavy heart to find comfort in the stillness of the evening. You have done enough for one day and you should be proud.",
        "Motivation:- Even the strongest warriors need to lay down their shields and sleep. Your resilience will be even more powerful after you find some rest.",
        "Motivation:- Listen to the quiet whispers of your body asking for a moment of calm. Giving yourself grace is the ultimate act of self-love today.",
        "Motivation:- You don't have to figure everything out while you are feeling this drained. The answers will come more clearly once you have closed your eyes.",
        "Motivation:- It is brave to admit when you are tired and need to slow down. Protecting your energy is the best way to ensure your future success.",
        "Motivation:- Small steps forward are still progress even if you feel like you are crawling. Be patient with your soul while it finds its strength again.",
        "Motivation:- The world can wait for a few hours while you focus on your own healing. You are the most important project you will ever work on.",
        "Motivation:- Every flower needs rain and every person needs a time of deep rest. Trust that this period of tiredness is preparing you for a bloom.",
        "Motivation:- You have a heart that feels deeply and that is a truly wonderful gift. Don't let exhaustion convince you that your sensitivity is a burden.",
        "Motivation:- Deep breathing can help settle the waves of emotion inside your tired mind. Just breathe and remember that you are safe in this moment.",
        "Motivation:- You are much more than the work you produce or the tasks you finish. Your existence is valuable simply because of the light you carry.",
        "Motivation:- It is okay to feel overwhelmed when you have been carrying so much weight. Set the heavy bags down and allow yourself to simply exist.",
        "Motivation:- Tomorrow's sun will rise and bring new opportunities for your happiness. For now let the darkness be a soft blanket for your weary eyes.",
        "Motivation:- You have survived 100% of your hardest days even when you felt this way. You are a survivor and your current fatigue is only temporary.",
        "Motivation:- Be gentle with your thoughts as you navigate through this low energy. You are doing a great job even if it feels difficult right now.",
        "Motivation:- Your energy is a limited resource that deserves to be managed with care. Saying no to extra stress is saying yes to your own well-being.",
        "Motivation:- Sometimes the most productive thing you can do is absolutely nothing at all. Silence is a medicine that heals the tired and emotional heart.",
        "Motivation:- You are allowed to be a work in progress and take as much time as you need. There is no race to the finish line of your personal growth.",
        "Motivation:- Trust that the universe will hold everything together while you take a nap. You are supported by forces much larger than your current worries.",
        "Motivation:- The heaviness in your chest will lift once you give yourself permission to let go. Release the pressure to be perfect and just be yourself.",
        "Motivation:- Your sensitivity is a superpower that allows you to connect with the world. Take care of that power by giving it the rest it requires.",
        "Motivation:- Look back at how far you have come since you first started this path. You are a mountain of strength even when you feel like a valley.",
        "Motivation:- Everything feels a little more manageable after a long and deep sleep. Trust the healing power of rest to fix your current perspective.",
        "Motivation:- You are a precious soul who is deserving of comfort and sweet dreams. Let the stress of the day fade away into the quiet of the night.",
        "Motivation:- It is okay to feel tired of being strong all the time for everyone else. Today is your turn to be looked after and to feel cared for.",
